{
  "text": ". This expression is valid given that the fixed point equation, (4) has a global attractor. We prove this in Proposition 1. We ignore the slow start phase and ignore that there may be an upper bound on the maximum window size. These assumptions are also made by [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "9391153",
